snippet.title: Whisker Squadron: Survivor Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
From the creators of RACE THE SUN - Whisker Squadron: Survivor is the first of two games in the Whisker Squadron universe. An on-rails shooter featuring wild 30-minute runs that play out across 10 increasingly frantic zones, featuring feline pilots. Coming to Steam August 21


Trailer animation by DCell, final edit by Jin Li
